OL,3,CBacup residents against council's
OL,4,Cplans to redevelop waste transfer
OL,5,Cstation
OL,7,FResidents in Bacup are protesting
OL,8,Fagainst Rossendale Council's plans to
OL,9,Fbuild a new 50,000-tonne-a-year-
OL,10,Fcapacity waste disposal unit in the
OL,11,Ftown centre.
OL,13,FThere is already a waste transfer site
OL,14,Fon the proposed location but the new
OL,15,Fbuilding is due to be bigger.
OL,17,FCharlie Codd's back garden directly
OL,18,Ffaces the disposal unit and says he
OL,19,Fhas got used to the sights, sounds and
OL,20,Fsmells of the waste site.
OL,1,W~k4j5 hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}      G1/7
