OL,3,CBacup residents against council's
OL,4,Cplans to redevelop waste transfer
OL,5,Cstation
OL,7,FBut the council's plans are causing
OL,8,Fnew worries for him and his neighbours.
OL,10,F"There are a large concentration of
OL,11,Fhouses that will be affected by odour,
OL,12,Fbut also contaminated dust", Charlie
OL,13,Fsaid.
OL,15,FHe added: "They (the council) have
OL,16,Fsaid that the odour will be in low
OL,17,Fwind condition and the contminated
OL,18,Fdust will be in worse in high wind
OL,19,Fconditions.
