OL,5,Cstation
OL,7,F"In other words, whatever the wind
OL,8,Fconditions are, we'll be getting it
OL,9,Fone way or another."
OL,11,FThe Henrietta Street site is used for
OL,12,Fcollecting and sorting recyclable
OL,13,Fwaste.
OL,15,FThe council's proposing a new waste
OL,16,Ftransfer building at the site, which
OL,17,Fwill allow it to meet a Government
OL,18,Frequirement to collect food waste
OL,19,Fseparately from other household waste.
OL,1,W~k4j5 hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}      G3/7
