OL,5,Cstation
OL,7,FBut residents fear the plans will lead
OL,8,Fto more lorries delivering and
OL,9,Fcollecting waste from the site - and
OL,10,Fmore disruption to their lives.
OL,12,FLynda Melvin who lives nearby said
OL,13,F"The smells, the flies, the rats,
OL,14,Fwhich we've already had, and what it's
OL,15,Fgoing to do to the town centre, it's
OL,16,Fsupposed to be a heritage town and
OL,17,Fthey are doing all these improvements.
OL,1,W~k4j5 hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}      G4/7
