OL,7,F"We have Bacup Pride, Cleaning all up,
OL,8,Fand it's just going to be worse than
OL,9,Fever."JResidents made their feelings
OL,10,Fknown at a peaceful protest outside
OL,11,Fthe council office on Friday 3rd
OL,12,FJanuary.
OL,14,FRossendale council has defended the
OL,15,Fplans, insisting they won't lead to
OL,16,Fany increase in the amount of waste it
OL,17,Fhandles.
OL,1,W~k4j5 hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}      G5/7
