OL,7,FCouncillor Alyson Barnes, Leader,
OL,8,FRossendale Council said " We're not
OL,9,Fchanging anything, we're still going
OL,10,Fto be processing the same waste from
OL,11,Fthe same households. We're just going
OL,12,Fto be sorting it differently.
OL,14,F"I would like to reassure residents
OL,15,Fthat we are looking to improve what
OL,16,Fthey are already.
